NoteBlock
  EPL Self-Hosted Test Suite
  Tests core language features using Assert statements
End

Assert 1 + 1 == 2
Assert 10 - 3 == 7
Assert 4 * 5 == 20
Assert 10 / 2 == 5
Assert 10 % 3 == 1
Assert 2 ** 3 == 8

x = 42
Assert x == 42
x = 100
Assert x == 100

name = "EPL"
Assert length(name) == 3

Assert true == true
Assert false == false

items = [1, 2, 3]
Assert length(items) == 3
Assert items[0] == 1
Assert items[2] == 3

Assert 10 > 5
Assert 3 < 8
Assert 5 == 5
Assert 5 != 3

result = 0
If true then
    result = 1
End
Assert result == 1

total = 0
For i from 1 to 5
    Increase total by i
End
Assert total == 15

Function double takes n
    Return n * 2
End
r1 = call double with 5
Assert r1 == 10
r2 = call double with 0
Assert r2 == 0

Say "All 20 self-hosted EPL tests passed!"
